---
title: Creamy Chicken Curry with Mangetout and Fluffy Rice
description: It’s no coincidence that Chef Mimi’s creamy curry is packed with crunchy mangetout beans. ‘Mange Tout’ in French means ‘eat it all’ and that’s just want you’ll want to do with this great dish. Packing a serious flavour punch from our specially made Sri Lankan spice blend, and made perfectly creamy by the addition of Mimi’s favourite ingredient, greek yoghurt, this is the perfect thing to enjoy for your next curry night.
